title: Zupa
typeOfFood: Lacto, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, European, Polish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small soup restaurant tucked in a little corner outside Rynek, the central Market Square. Every day a selection of 8 to 10 soups, with around 4 marked vegetarian (wege), of which 1 or 2 are vegan, but you must ask to be sure. Dine-in at the small counter seating area is available for about 5 people. Also has outlets at Igielna 14 and Bujwida 25.
